He has over twenty eight years of experience in the investment industry. Prior to joining The Swarthmore Group in 2005, he spent seven years as a Senior Portfolio Manager with Automatic Data Processing, where he was responsible for $7.5 billion in fixed income assets and investing and funding payroll float balances that periodically would exceed $10 billion. Mr. DeLaney's experience also includes being a member of SEI's Global Fixed Income Management Unit, and serving as portfolio manager with The Fairfield Group, Independence Capital Management Inc. and Parkway Management Corporation. Types of portfolios managed include: pension, savings bank, insurance company, bond proceeds, money market and mutual fund accounts. Mr. DeLaney holds a B.A. in Economics from Bucknell University. He has earned the right to use the Chartered Financial Analyst (CFA) designation.TaxesTax ServicesSend to PhoneSwarthmore Group Inc1717 Arch St Ste 3810, Philadelphia, PA 19103(215) 557-9300Send this business listing as a text message to a mobile phone.I agree to the Terms and ConditionsCancelSendYour text message was sent.To opt out at anytime, send the word STOP to YP411.To get a help message, send the word HELP to YP411.There was an error sending your text.Please try again.E-MailSwarthmore Group Inc1717 Arch St Ste 3810, Philadelphia, PA 19103(215) 557-9300Send this business details to yourself or up to 5 friends.Up to 5 email addresses, separate addresses with a commaSend Yourself a CopyCancelSend 
